content_sections.content:
Learn how to create different dividers with CSS.
Dashed
Dotted
Solid
Rounded

How To Create Dividers
Step 1) Add HTML:
Example
<hr class="dashed">
<hr class="dotted">
<hr class="solid">
<hr 
  class="rounded">
Step 2) Add CSS:
Example
/* Dashed border */
hr.dashed {
border-top: 3px dashed #bbb;
}
/* Dotted border */
hr.dotted {
border-top: 3px dotted #bbb;
}
/* Solid border */
hr.solid {
border-top: 3px solid #bbb;
}
/* Rounded border */
hr.rounded {
border-top: 8px solid #bbb;
border-radius: 5px;
}

